Name: DogFight Time
About the game: Dogfight Time is an aerial racing game with shooting mechanics. Race your opponents into the finish line, picking up objects to destroy opponents planes or protecting your plane from damage. Earn in-game money by completing matches, unlock new planes to race with. Try different Modes from championship to timed races. Bored to play alone? worry not, you can use split screen to play with anyone you like.
